00:32:00.730 --> 00:32:04.900 align:middle line:90%
I think that's very important.

00:32:04.900 --> 00:32:09.250 align:middle line:84%
I've now seen many, many
people with very wide states

00:32:09.250 --> 00:32:10.810 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness.

00:32:10.810 --> 00:32:16.880 align:middle line:84%
You just cannot explain this
on a simple neurophysiological

00:32:16.880 --> 00:32:17.680 align:middle line:90%
principle.

00:32:17.680 --> 00:32:20.370 align:middle line:90%


00:32:20.370 --> 00:32:23.820 align:middle line:84%
>> What we find with research
done in hospitals now is that

00:32:23.820 --> 00:32:27.720 align:middle line:84%
people who are clearly in
cardiac arrest are experiencing

00:32:27.720 --> 00:32:30.130 align:middle line:84%
