00:32:30.130 --> 00:32:32.550 align:middle line:84%
which really contradicts
our understanding,

00:32:32.550 --> 00:32:36.030 align:middle line:84%
or the current materialist
perspective that the brain

00:32:36.030 --> 00:32:37.550 align:middle line:90%
produces consciousness.

00:32:37.550 --> 00:32:40.900 align:middle line:90%


00:32:40.900 --> 00:32:44.200 align:middle line:84%
>> The argument is, yes, the
brain is disturbed somehow.

00:32:44.200 --> 00:32:46.690 align:middle line:90%
But the brain isn't functioning.

00:32:46.690 --> 00:32:48.460 align:middle line:90%
Oh, yes, it is, they say.

00:32:48.460 --> 00:32:50.590 align:middle line:90%
Little bit just around the back.

00:32:50.590 --> 00:32:51.410 align:middle line:90%
Rubbish.

00:32:51.410 --> 00:32:53.624 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:32:53.624 --> 00:32:56.040 align:middle line:84%
To get these very
wide experiences,

00:32:56.040 --> 00:32:59.340 align:middle line:84%
you have to have many areas of
the brain functioning properly

00:32:59.340 --> 00:33:02.180 align:middle line:90%
or it's somewhere else.

00:33:02.180 --> 00:33:05.580 align:middle line:90%
And I think it somewhere else.

00:33:05.580 --> 00:33:07.590 align:middle line:84%
>> Consciousness
