But there is also our own
individual consciousness,

00:33:14.610 --> 00:33:16.980 align:middle line:84%
which can't be separated from
fundamental consciousness

00:33:16.980 --> 00:33:20.010 align:middle line:84%
because our own individual
consciousness is

00:33:20.010 --> 00:33:23.508 align:middle line:84%
an influx, you could say, of
fundamental consciousness.

00:33:23.508 --> 00:33:26.320 align:middle line:90%


00:33:26.320 --> 00:33:28.510 align:middle line:90%
>> The body is an avatar.

00:33:28.510 --> 00:33:30.295 align:middle line:90%
Consciousness is the player.

00:33:30.295 --> 00:33:35.410 align:middle line:90%


00:33:35.410 --> 00:33:39.340 align:middle line:84%
