It's just information,
just like in our reality.

00:33:52.420 --> 00:33:55.050 align:middle line:10%
So that gets us to the
point of understanding

00:33:55.050 --> 00:33:57.930 align:middle line:10%
that consciousness
is not in the body.

00:33:57.930 --> 00:33:59.335 align:middle line:10%
It's separate from the body.

00:33:59.335 --> 00:34:00.135 align:middle line:10%
It's the player.

00:34:00.135 --> 00:34:04.370 align:middle line:90%


00:34:04.370 --> 00:34:06.810 align:middle line:84%
>> We normally
think of the self,

00:34:06.810 --> 00:34:09.690 align:middle line:84%
or feel that the
self is a me in here,

00:34:09.690 --> 00:34:10.929 align:middle line:90%
