00:34:19.350 --> 00:34:20.750 align:middle line:90%
everything else.

00:34:20.750 --> 00:34:22.280 align:middle line:84%
There can't be
somebody in there.

00:34:22.280 --> 00:34:24.409 align:middle line:84%
