brain where we can be,

00:34:24.409 --> 00:34:26.100 align:middle line:90%
and so on, and so on.

00:34:26.100 --> 00:34:28.710 align:middle line:84%
>> There isn't anything
out there, or in here.

00:34:28.710 --> 00:34:29.820 align:middle line:90%
This is the confusion.

00:34:29.820 --> 00:34:33.210 align:middle line:90%


00:34:33.210 --> 00:34:34.719 align:middle line:90%
It's all the same thing.

00:34:34.719 --> 00:34:36.500 align:middle line:84%
