mind, by consciousness.

00:34:40.557 --> 00:34:44.380 align:middle line:90%


00:34:44.380 --> 00:34:48.219 align:middle line:84%
>> So I think the main role
of the brain is not to produce

00:34:48.219 --> 00:34:53.320 align:middle line:84%
consciousness, but to canalize
or transmit fundamental

00:34:53.320 --> 00:34:55.900 align:middle line:84%
consciousness into
our individual being.

00:34:55.900 --> 00:35:10.290 align:middle line:90%


00:35:10.290 --> 00:35:12.460 align:middle line:84%
>> People experience
them all the time,

00:35:12.460 --> 00:35:14.040 align:middle line:90%
right across the world.

00:35:14.040 --> 00:35:15.990 align:middle line:84%
